=================================================================================
RECOMMENDED LICENSES FOR AI QUICKSTARTS
=================================================================================

1. Apache License 2.0 (RECOMMENDED for most quickstarts)
   - Permissive license
   - Allows commercial use
   - Provides patent protection
   - Compatible with Red Hat projects
   - Download from: https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0.txt

2. MIT License
   - Very permissive and simple
   - Allows commercial use
   - Minimal restrictions
   - Download from: https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT


=================================================================================
HOW TO ADD YOUR LICENSE
=================================================================================

Step 1: Choose a license from the list above (Apache 2.0 recommended)

Step 2: Download the full license text from the provided URL

Step 3: Replace this ENTIRE file with the license text

Step 4: If the license requires it (like Apache 2.0), add copyright information:
        Copyright [YEAR] [COPYRIGHT HOLDER]

Step 5: Verify the LICENSE file is in the root of your repository

